{
  "stem": "11174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was taken up by the house-- around the house, although we had a maid all the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And but there was one thing that now it's a forgotten thing, you know, of mending, mending socks, for instance.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took a little while.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or mending some-- some clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was here and there a little hole and doesn't mean you throw it away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You make a patch, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was already in our house which I told you that we were considered the upper-middle class.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was a normal routine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a maid already so that didn't mean that but that poor, but there still is the normal routine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What do you mean you're going to throw away something that only needs a patch?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So and she also liked very much with, with charity.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was-- this was in the summertime especially, there were Jewish-- Jewish poor people that went-- whole families in their wagon, a few families in a wagon and there were never-- the very lowest class.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some people were afraid that they'll steal when they come into the house and they don't let them into the house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Only when they came, they gave them the few cents and go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother, this is summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was occupied almost everyday with this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Couldn't take that and couldn't accept it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was on the oven standing two pots, two black iron pots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One was with coffee and one was with what we call [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That means a potato soup and everybody-- and our table was always spread bread with butter so everybody came in in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Here is a plate of soup, bread and butter, as much as they have desired.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
